## PS5 Wireless Controller ##

## Joypad Up. Down. Left. Right ##
ABS_HAT0X CONTROLLER_BUTTON_LEFT CONTROLLER_BUTTON_RIGHT
ABS_HAT0Y CONTROLLER_BUTTON_UP CONTROLLER_BUTTON_DOWN

## Left and Right Analogue joysticks ##
ABS_X CONTROLLER_ANALOGUE_X
ABS_Y CONTROLLER_ANALOGUE_Y
ABS_RX CONTROLLER_ANALOGUE_Z
ABS_RY CONTROLLER_ANALOGUE_T

## 4 main pad buttons ##
BTN_SOUTH CONTROLLER_BUTTON_A
BTN_EAST CONTROLLER_BUTTON_D
BTN_NORTH CONTROLLER_BUTTON_B
BTN_WEST CONTROLLER_BUTTON_C

## Top 4 Single and Analogue buttons ## 
BTN_TL CONTROLLER_BUTTON_E
BTN_TR CONTROLLER_BUTTON_F
ABS_Z CONTROLLER_ANALOGUE_R
ABS_RZ CONTROLLER_ANALOGUE_L

## Left and Right analogue buttons ##
BTN_THUMBL CONTROLLER_BUTTON_H
BTN_THUMBR CONTROLLER_BUTTON_COIN

## 3 Main PS5 Service buttons. PSLogo, Start and Select buttons ##
BTN_SELECT CONTROLLER_BUTTON_SERVICE
BTN_START CONTROLLER_BUTTON_START
BTN_MODE CONTROLLER_BUTTON_TEST
